  (3)solicit or induce any party to a contract lease or agreement to break such contract for the
purpose of substituting a new contract lease or agreement when such soliciting or inducing is
motivated by anticipated personal gain;

    (ii)advertising or offering “free appraisals” unless the advertiser is equipped and stands
ready to appraise real estate to any person requesting such an appraisal free of charge,
